   <talk_paragraph index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting-a" mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>The betrayer came from the Order again.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting-b" mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>How did you try for it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting-c" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>But nobody knows that the Dragon Follower was in the order.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting-d" mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>Isn't there a proven way to eliminate them?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Enoch$<BR>Dragon Followers are mankind's betrayers. It is so shameful that we are of the same kind.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Enoch$<BR>Please don't mention anything about it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Enoch$<BR>
We sent secret police called 'Goddess' Eye' to seek information of the betrayers. But it was so hard to arrest them because they were operating alone.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Enoch$<BR>
They are sneaky people. I had no idea that they were amongst us for so long. At least, the betrayer Ignacio pretended to show a deep faith.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n046_cleric_master_enoc-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Enoch$<BR>
An eye for an eye. A tooth for a tooth. We are planning to plant a spy in the Followers and destroy their leaders.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
